snippet.title: Diana and Roma Magic Colored playhouse challenge
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma turn small playhouses into huge playhouse. Children decorate them with colorful furniture using magic. How much fun it is to play in four colored houses! But the magic wand falls into Oliver's hands.
Thanks for watching!
